<p>After completion of writing your content, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Commit changes</code> as shown below.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/blog/2019-09-05/6.PNG" alt="" /></p>

<p>Now, go to settings and scroll down to Github pages you will find a link in which your page is hosted.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/blog/2019-09-05/7.PNG" alt="" /></p>

